description: Gets a pre-signed S3 write URL that you use to upload the zip archive when importing a bot or a bot locale.

nested_items.name: importId
nested_items.description: An identifier for a unique import job. Use it when you call the StartImport operation.

nested_items.name: uploadUrl
nested_items.description: A pre-signed S3 write URL. Upload the zip archive file that contains the definition of your bot or bot locale.
